# Mo Conventionalcell
# Generates a 2 atom Mo_primitvecell with the multiplicity of 1:1:1 (x:y:z), and computes the band structure.

#Dataset 2 : the band structure
 iscf    -2
 getden  -1  # get charge density from the 1st run
 kptopt   0 # band structure plot with 5 intervals
 #ndivsm   1 # number of divisors for each interval
#ndivk      260*1 #Number of DIVisions of K lines
nkpt  261
kpt 
